WEBVTT

00:01.752 --> 00:03.044
[ mouse squeaks ]

00:03.128 --> 00:04.420
[ penguins wenk ]

00:06.590 --> 00:07.548
[ all cheering ]

00:10.761 --> 00:11.719
[ screeches ]

00:13.347 --> 00:14.597
♪ Adventure Time ♪

00:14.681 --> 00:15.932
♪ Come on, grab your friends ♪

00:16.015 --> 00:18.601
♪ We'll go to very distant lands ♪

00:18.685 --> 00:21.103
♪ With Jake the dog and Finn the Human ♪

00:21.188 --> 00:22.605
♪ The fun will never end ♪

00:22.689 --> 00:24.398
♪ lt's Adventure Time ♪

00:26.000 --> 00:32.073
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:35.410 --> 00:36.202
Hey, Jake?

00:36.286 --> 00:37.078
Yeah?

00:37.162 --> 00:37.995
You ever wonder what a

00:38.080 --> 00:39.205
demon's heart looks like?

00:39.289 --> 00:40.206
Of course, dude.

00:40.290 --> 00:41.415
You ever wonder what a

00:41.500 --> 00:42.458
demon's heart tastes like?

00:42.543 --> 00:45.753
Hey, kid, you want some magic powers?

00:45.837 --> 00:48.798
Magic powers for absolutely free.

00:48.882 --> 00:49.924
Heck yeah!

00:50.008 --> 00:50.841
Wait!

00:50.926 --> 00:52.093
Let's not be too rash.

00:52.177 --> 00:53.427
Just look at this guy.

00:53.512 --> 00:56.430
Check out the sunken, lifeless eyes,

00:56.515 --> 00:59.267
the foul stench of decay.

00:59.351 --> 01:00.685
You know what that means?

01:00.769 --> 01:02.812
lt means he's evil, I guess.

01:02.896 --> 01:04.438
Well, evil, sure, but

01:04.522 --> 01:06.023
mostly, he's unattractive, and

01:06.108 --> 01:08.025
unattractive people are desperate.

01:08.110 --> 01:09.527
You should haggle with him.

01:09.611 --> 01:11.112
Hey, I want more than

01:11.196 --> 01:12.113
just free powers.

01:12.197 --> 01:13.197
What else you got?

01:13.282 --> 01:14.407
All right.

01:15.158 --> 01:18.828
Free magical powers and...
[ cracking ]

01:18.912 --> 01:19.829
...and this keychain.

01:19.913 --> 01:21.080
Oh, oh, oh!

01:21.164 --> 01:22.665
Play it cool, Finn.

01:22.749 --> 01:23.666
Right.

01:23.750 --> 01:25.668
l begrudgingly accept your offer.

01:25.752 --> 01:26.544
Yes!

01:26.628 --> 01:28.546
Then the deal is struck.

01:28.630 --> 01:30.381
[ laughs evilly ]

01:30.465 --> 01:31.882
You can pick up your powers

01:31.967 --> 01:34.885
right through that door.

01:34.970 --> 01:37.638
This way.

01:39.474 --> 01:43.394
[ wind howling ]

01:43.478 --> 01:44.312
[ pbht! ]

01:44.396 --> 01:45.354
[ grunts ]

01:45.439 --> 01:46.689
This place looks magical.

01:46.773 --> 01:48.316
You think this is where we get the powers?

01:48.400 --> 01:50.109
Yes, I do.

01:50.193 --> 01:52.236
Free powers for all.

01:52.321 --> 01:53.112
Want some?

01:53.196 --> 01:54.030
Yeah!

01:54.114 --> 01:55.990
Are you the guy handing them out?

01:56.074 --> 01:59.118
You seek Bufo the Wizard.

01:59.202 --> 02:00.578
So, where is that guy?

02:00.662 --> 02:01.996
He is here, of course.

02:02.080 --> 02:02.872
Uh...

02:02.956 --> 02:03.998
He's here?

02:04.082 --> 02:05.041
But he's not you?

02:05.125 --> 02:06.042
That's right.

02:06.126 --> 02:07.710
We should beat him up

02:07.794 --> 02:09.336
until he starts making sense.

02:09.420 --> 02:11.005
[ groans ]

02:11.089 --> 02:13.507
ALL:
We are Bufo.

02:13.592 --> 02:15.343
Oh!

02:15.427 --> 02:16.552
ALL: [ echoing ]
So... So...

02:16.637 --> 02:17.720
ALL:
...you wish to be

02:17.804 --> 02:19.013
inducted into the ancient --

02:19.097 --> 02:20.056
...ancient order --

02:20.140 --> 02:21.015
Dang it, Leonard.

02:21.099 --> 02:22.350
lfwe don't talk at the same

02:22.434 --> 02:24.352
time, nobody can understand us.

02:24.436 --> 02:25.478
Sorry. Geez.

02:25.562 --> 02:26.479
ALL:
Ahem!

02:26.563 --> 02:30.149
So, you want free wizard powers,

02:30.233 --> 02:32.485
powers like...these!

02:32.569 --> 02:33.778
[ laughs ]
Yeah!

02:33.862 --> 02:34.695
Yeah!

02:34.780 --> 02:35.905
BOTH:
We want them.

02:35.989 --> 02:36.906
Give us the stuff.

02:36.990 --> 02:38.616
- Yes, we do.
- Can't wait.

02:38.700 --> 02:41.077
ALL:
Then follow me.

02:41.161 --> 02:42.745
BOTH:
Whoo-hoo!

02:42.829 --> 02:46.332
ALL:
Behold the grand hall of wizardry.

02:46.416 --> 02:48.626
This is where young potentials

02:48.710 --> 02:51.087
train to become ultimate wizards.

02:51.171 --> 02:52.630
But most are not ready for the

02:52.714 --> 02:54.548
responsibility that comes with it.

02:54.633 --> 02:56.092
l'm responsible, dude.

02:56.176 --> 02:57.051
So am l.

02:57.135 --> 02:58.260
That's a lie.

02:58.345 --> 02:59.553
lt is a lie.

02:59.638 --> 03:01.931
And I take full responsibility for it.

03:02.015 --> 03:04.392
ALL:
Yes, yes, very responsible.

03:04.476 --> 03:07.395
Now l bestow upon you these...

03:07.479 --> 03:09.730
wizard cloaks!

03:09.815 --> 03:11.065
BOTH:
Whoa!

03:11.149 --> 03:13.484
Hey, this is a dress.

03:13.568 --> 03:16.070
Yeah. And l am into it.

03:16.154 --> 03:17.571
lt's like gossamer.

03:17.656 --> 03:19.907
[ grunting ]

03:19.991 --> 03:21.951
This way, l won't be embarrassed.

03:22.035 --> 03:23.077
ALL:
Fine, fine.

03:23.161 --> 03:25.579
Now, for every power that you

03:25.664 --> 03:28.207
accrue, you shall receive a star

03:28.291 --> 03:29.709
badge like these.

03:29.793 --> 03:31.877
This final star betokens the

03:31.962 --> 03:34.505
rank of ultimate wizard.

03:34.589 --> 03:36.173
BOTH:
Whoa!

03:36.258 --> 03:37.508
Mark me, Jake.

03:37.592 --> 03:39.135
l shall have that final star.

03:39.219 --> 03:40.219
Where do we start?

03:40.303 --> 03:42.847
ALL:
Level 1 -- Dustomancy.

03:42.931 --> 03:43.764
Yeah!

03:43.849 --> 03:45.224
Dustomancy, whatever that is.

03:45.308 --> 03:47.101
Gimme, gimme, gimme, gimme, gimme!

03:47.185 --> 03:48.644
ALL:
To receive this power,

03:48.729 --> 03:50.271
you must first...

03:50.355 --> 03:52.648
eat these brooms.

03:52.733 --> 03:53.691
[ zip! zip! ]

03:53.775 --> 03:55.109
All right.

03:55.193 --> 03:56.485
[ gags ]
Wait.

03:56.570 --> 03:57.361
[ spits ]

03:57.446 --> 03:58.529
This is gross.

03:58.613 --> 04:00.156
Man, l can't eat this.

04:00.240 --> 04:01.365
Yeah, you can.

04:01.450 --> 04:02.241
Do what l do.

04:02.325 --> 04:04.118
[ growls ]

04:04.202 --> 04:05.786
Ahh!

04:05.871 --> 04:06.787
[ gulps ]

04:06.872 --> 04:08.080
[ squeak! ]

04:08.165 --> 04:08.998
Oops.

04:09.082 --> 04:10.499
Ah, there we go.

04:10.584 --> 04:11.792
[ both gasp ]

04:11.877 --> 04:13.377
Whoa, you got a star.

04:13.462 --> 04:14.587
[ chuckles ]

04:14.671 --> 04:15.671
Observe my magics.

04:15.756 --> 04:16.839
Wait, Jake.

04:16.923 --> 04:19.007
Don't use them until l finish my broom.

04:19.091 --> 04:21.010
[ growling ]

04:21.094 --> 04:22.178
[ gulps ]

04:22.262 --> 04:24.305
Last...bite.

04:24.389 --> 04:25.222
[ gulps ]

04:25.307 --> 04:28.142
Dude, you got your star, too.

04:28.226 --> 04:30.144
We're Dustomancers!

04:30.228 --> 04:32.021
[ grunts ]

04:32.105 --> 04:33.355
Nothing happened.

04:33.440 --> 04:35.149
This is a total rip-off.

04:35.233 --> 04:36.734
Bufo, you tricked us.

04:36.818 --> 04:38.986
Stupid power doesn't even work.

04:39.070 --> 04:40.738
ALL:
Calm yourself, boy.

04:40.822 --> 04:42.323
You are acting hysterical.

04:42.407 --> 04:44.074
Do you not see that you are

04:44.159 --> 04:45.576
using Dustomancy?

04:45.660 --> 04:46.619
Behold.

04:46.703 --> 04:49.121
l'm doing this?

04:49.206 --> 04:50.790
So...I have --

04:50.874 --> 04:52.291
ALL:
Yes!

04:52.375 --> 04:55.211
Mastery over all dust motes.

04:55.295 --> 04:57.630
You can also read their emotions.

04:57.714 --> 04:59.715
For instance, this mote is very

04:59.800 --> 05:01.425
unhappy in his marriage.

05:01.510 --> 05:03.552
That's...sort of cool.

05:03.637 --> 05:05.054
Sort of cool?

05:05.138 --> 05:06.263
This is radical!

05:06.348 --> 05:07.723
Whoo, yeah!

05:07.808 --> 05:09.266
Force that enthusiasm.

05:09.351 --> 05:11.644
ALL:
Are you ready for more magic?

05:11.728 --> 05:12.978
We get more?

05:13.063 --> 05:14.980
ALL:
So much more.

05:15.065 --> 05:17.399
Like level 2 -- the power of

05:17.484 --> 05:18.317
shadowcery.

05:18.401 --> 05:20.736
You can't see through those, right?

05:20.821 --> 05:22.321
Nope, not at all.

05:22.405 --> 05:24.073
ALL:
To gain provenance over

05:24.157 --> 05:25.783
the shadows, place your hands

05:25.867 --> 05:26.742
into this bowl.

05:26.827 --> 05:27.910
What bowl?

05:27.994 --> 05:29.578
ALL:
No! Cover your eyes!

05:29.663 --> 05:31.080
[ groans ]
Fine.

05:31.164 --> 05:32.832
ALL:
Thrust your hands into

05:32.916 --> 05:34.834
this bowl... of eyeballs.

05:34.918 --> 05:35.793
Eyeballs?!

05:35.877 --> 05:37.044
Dude, it's okay.

05:37.128 --> 05:38.087
They're just peeled grapes.

05:38.171 --> 05:38.963
ALL:
No!

05:39.047 --> 05:41.382
They're eyeballs.

05:41.466 --> 05:42.299
[ giggle ]

05:42.384 --> 05:43.342
Yuck!

05:43.426 --> 05:44.677
ALL:
Well done.

05:44.761 --> 05:48.347
You have groped the eyeballs fearlessly.

05:48.431 --> 05:51.350
Another star! Yeah!

05:51.434 --> 05:52.852
Shadowcery.

05:52.936 --> 05:54.353
[ horse neighs, grunts ]

05:54.437 --> 05:56.689
Onward, my shadow steed.

05:56.773 --> 05:57.690
Huh?

05:57.774 --> 05:59.149
No touchies.

05:59.234 --> 06:02.403
Wizard powers are so cool.

06:02.487 --> 06:06.782
l want all the star badges!

06:06.867 --> 06:09.785
ALL:
Excellent.

06:09.870 --> 06:12.246
[ laughs ]

06:12.330 --> 06:14.248
[ cling! cling! cling! ]

06:14.332 --> 06:15.708
ALL:
Well done.

06:15.792 --> 06:17.167
[ laughs ]

06:17.252 --> 06:19.169
[ both gulping ]

06:19.254 --> 06:21.338
[ whoosh! ]

06:21.423 --> 06:26.343
[ mumbles ]

06:26.428 --> 06:29.513
[ whoosh! whoosh! ]

06:29.598 --> 06:31.348
[ shing! ]

06:31.433 --> 06:33.183
Whoo-hoo-hoo!

06:33.268 --> 06:35.352
Whoa!

06:35.437 --> 06:37.479
All we're missing now is the big star.

06:37.564 --> 06:39.481
You ready to complete the set, man?

06:39.566 --> 06:40.774
Nah, l'm good.

06:40.859 --> 06:41.692
What?!

06:41.776 --> 06:42.860
How can you stop now?

06:42.944 --> 06:44.445
Eh, l got everything I

06:44.529 --> 06:45.946
need -- a limitless supply of

06:46.031 --> 06:47.573
mayonnaise, this captivating new

06:47.657 --> 06:49.074
hairstyle, and I just learned

06:49.159 --> 06:50.284
the best spell of all.

06:50.368 --> 06:51.410
What's that?

06:51.494 --> 06:52.703
Sleep.

06:52.787 --> 06:53.704
[ snoring ]

06:53.788 --> 06:55.706
Aw, what a lame-o.

06:55.790 --> 06:58.626
Bufo, I'm ready to get that big star.

06:58.710 --> 07:00.294
ALL:
To tell true, the last

07:00.378 --> 07:01.337
power is not free.

07:01.421 --> 07:02.338
Wha?

07:02.422 --> 07:04.006
You can't do this to me, man.

07:04.090 --> 07:05.090
l've got no money.

07:05.175 --> 07:06.592
ALL:
No. No cash.

07:06.676 --> 07:08.552
For the final star, you must

07:08.637 --> 07:11.472
take... the pledge of ultimate responsibility.

07:11.556 --> 07:13.599
Okay, I'll take that pledge.

07:13.683 --> 07:14.475
ALL:
Are you sure?

07:14.559 --> 07:16.393
Perhaps you are not
sufficiently familiar with --

07:16.478 --> 07:17.311
l'm ready.

07:17.395 --> 07:18.354
ALL:
Well, there may be

07:18.438 --> 07:20.022
ramifications that you cannot --

07:20.106 --> 07:21.273
just let me take that

07:21.358 --> 07:22.274
pledge, man!

07:22.359 --> 07:23.901
ALL:
My word, I've never met

07:23.985 --> 07:26.195
someone so irresponsibly responsible.

07:26.279 --> 07:27.279
Very well, then.

07:27.364 --> 07:29.949
You must...grasp...my hand.

07:30.033 --> 07:31.617
That's it? Easy.

07:31.701 --> 07:32.743
Whoa!

07:32.827 --> 07:34.411
[ groans ]

07:34.496 --> 07:35.412
Huh?

07:35.497 --> 07:38.415
[ gasps ]
My big star!

07:38.500 --> 07:41.585
Yes! Whoo-hoo! Yeah!

07:41.670 --> 07:42.711
Wait. Where am l?

07:42.796 --> 07:44.546
ALL:
Direct your attention to

07:44.631 --> 07:45.756
the scale-model orb.

07:45.840 --> 07:46.757
Huh?

07:46.841 --> 07:48.467
ls that an asteroid heading for

07:48.551 --> 07:49.468
this very temple?

07:49.552 --> 07:50.469
ALL:
Yes.

07:50.553 --> 07:52.054
lt's been heading for this

07:52.138 --> 07:54.348
temple for 847 years.

07:54.432 --> 07:56.308
Only the magic of the ultimate

07:56.393 --> 07:59.061
wizards keeps it from
getting any closer.

07:59.145 --> 08:02.398
Quickly, add your power
to that of the orb.

08:02.482 --> 08:03.482
Oh, okay.

08:03.566 --> 08:04.483
Whoa!

08:04.567 --> 08:06.068
l got it. Now what?

08:06.152 --> 08:08.487
ALL:
Now l release the elder

08:08.571 --> 08:10.322
Jeremy from his pledge.

08:10.407 --> 08:11.448
Razzamafoo!

08:11.533 --> 08:13.117
lt's about time.

08:13.201 --> 08:15.577
ALL:
And you take his place

08:15.662 --> 08:18.372
for the rest of your natural life.

08:18.456 --> 08:19.373
Awesome.

08:19.457 --> 08:20.374
Wait. What?

08:20.458 --> 08:22.084
ALL:
This is what you signed

08:22.168 --> 08:23.585
up for when you took the...

08:23.670 --> 08:25.629
pledge of ultimate responsibility.

08:25.714 --> 08:27.256
This is what all the

08:27.340 --> 08:28.799
wizard training was about?

08:28.883 --> 08:30.050
You tricked me!

08:30.135 --> 08:31.343
OLD WlZARD:
Young wizard!

08:31.428 --> 08:33.178
The asteroid approaches.

08:33.263 --> 08:35.054
Oh, yeah, sorry.

08:35.140 --> 08:36.306
[ warble! warble! ]

08:36.390 --> 08:39.643
ALL:
l tricked you, of course, but would anyone ever

08:39.727 --> 08:41.645
volunteer to do this?

08:41.730 --> 08:43.647
l'm out.

08:43.732 --> 08:45.524
Aw, man, this sucks.

08:45.608 --> 08:46.775
[ groans ]

08:46.860 --> 08:49.069
Old people, there's got to be a better way.

08:49.154 --> 08:50.070
Nope.

08:50.155 --> 08:52.489
This is how the
ancient ones wanted it.

08:52.574 --> 08:53.407
Yeah?

08:53.491 --> 08:54.783
l got a younger idea.

08:54.868 --> 08:55.784
[ grunts ]

08:55.869 --> 08:56.952
You fool!

08:57.037 --> 08:59.204
Your newfangled thinking will

08:59.289 --> 09:00.831
get us all killed!

09:00.915 --> 09:03.167
Youth culture forever!

09:03.251 --> 09:04.168
Whoa!

09:04.252 --> 09:06.920
ALL:
Hey, have you gone crazy?

09:07.005 --> 09:09.298
Get back in the bouncy harness.

09:09.382 --> 09:10.549
Sleep.

09:10.633 --> 09:12.259
ALL:
You are -- [ moans ]

09:12.343 --> 09:13.927
[ snoring ]

09:14.012 --> 09:15.554
Ultimate wizardry,

09:15.638 --> 09:16.805
activate!

09:16.890 --> 09:17.973
Uh...hmm.

09:18.058 --> 09:20.309
Maybe my footing's off?

09:20.393 --> 09:22.853
There you go.

09:22.937 --> 09:26.648
l cast dragon eyes...

09:26.733 --> 09:28.484
tiger claw...

09:28.568 --> 09:30.319
vorpal hand...

09:30.403 --> 09:33.322
blazing feet...

09:33.406 --> 09:35.324
beauteous wings...

09:35.408 --> 09:38.035
and finally, every other power l

09:38.119 --> 09:40.496
didn't mention by name!

09:40.580 --> 09:42.414
With all my magics combined, l'm

09:42.499 --> 09:44.041
powerful enough to move the

09:44.125 --> 09:45.584
entire village out of the

09:45.668 --> 09:47.753
asteroid's path.

09:47.837 --> 09:50.089
[ straining ]

09:50.173 --> 09:52.424
[ snoring ]

09:52.509 --> 09:55.594
[ straining continues ]

09:55.678 --> 09:56.512
[ gasps ]

09:56.596 --> 09:58.055
l need some help.

09:58.139 --> 09:59.223
Jake, awaken!

09:59.307 --> 10:00.724
Reflect.

10:00.809 --> 10:02.017
Hey, I'm alive.

10:02.102 --> 10:03.477
What's that up there?

10:03.561 --> 10:04.686
[ gasps ]
Oh, no!

10:04.771 --> 10:06.522
Aw, my stupid young

10:06.606 --> 10:08.357
idea will be responsible for

10:08.441 --> 10:09.691
hundreds of deaths.

10:09.776 --> 10:10.692
OLD WlZARD:
lt sure will.

10:10.777 --> 10:11.610
Huh?

10:11.694 --> 10:13.278
Old wizards, you ditched your

10:13.363 --> 10:14.655
responsibilities to help me.

10:14.739 --> 10:15.656
What?! No!

10:15.740 --> 10:17.324
We left so we wouldn't be killed

10:17.408 --> 10:18.242
by that asteroid.

10:18.326 --> 10:19.243
Oh, okay.

10:19.327 --> 10:20.786
Um, since you're here already,

10:20.870 --> 10:23.455
can you lend me a hand?

10:23.540 --> 10:26.291
[ all straining ]

10:26.376 --> 10:27.793
[ zip! whoosh! ]

10:27.877 --> 10:28.836
[ snores ]

10:28.920 --> 10:29.711
[ whoosh! ]

10:29.796 --> 10:31.713
Huh?

10:31.798 --> 10:32.923
Whoo-hoo!

10:33.007 --> 10:33.924
Nice job.

10:34.008 --> 10:35.926
Thanks to us, the village is saved,

10:36.010 --> 10:37.469
and we reclaimed a few of

10:37.554 --> 10:38.512
your twilight years.

10:38.596 --> 10:40.013
ALL:
Don't forget to thank me,

10:40.098 --> 10:42.349
for this was my plan for

10:42.433 --> 10:44.643
all of these 847 years.

10:44.727 --> 10:45.727
No way.

10:45.812 --> 10:47.146
Your plan was to dupe a

10:47.230 --> 10:49.022
succession of rubes into keeping

10:49.107 --> 10:50.274
the asteroid at bay.

10:50.358 --> 10:52.109
ALL:
Perhaps you're right.

10:52.193 --> 10:53.986
No more giving out free powers.

10:54.070 --> 10:56.655
l hereby renounce all magic.

10:56.739 --> 10:59.658
[ sniffles, cries ]

10:59.742 --> 11:03.370
My life is over!!

11:03.454 --> 11:04.413
Chill, man.

11:04.497 --> 11:05.914
You don't have to quit yourjob.

11:05.999 --> 11:06.790
ALL:
l don't?

11:06.875 --> 11:07.958
Nah, just don't take

11:08.042 --> 11:09.960
credit for ideas that aren't yours.

11:10.044 --> 11:12.462
ALL:
Oh. Okay. Good idea.

11:12.547 --> 11:14.965
Glad I thought of it.

11:15.049 --> 11:17.634
Hey, naked kid, you want some

